{
  "id": "adv_card_mhk_04_02",
  "title": "miho 2話 想定外の事態です",
  "script": [
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_summerfes-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "summerfes-00-noon",
      "startTime": 0
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "mhk",
      "speakerName": "miho",
      "speakerNameEn": "miho",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-miho.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_mhk_04_02/sud_vo_adv_card_mhk_04_02-mhk001.m4a",
      "text": "すみませんが、{user}さん\nちょっと、海に行って来ていただけますか？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Excuse me‚ {user}-san.\nCould you go to the sea for a moment?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 2.7666666667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_mhk_04_02/sud_vo_adv_card_mhk_04_02-koh001.m4a",
      "text": "……ええと……え、俺がですか？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Uh… Wait‚ me?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 5.2517911911,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_summerfes-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "summerfes-00-noon",
      "startTime": 9.4026077271
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "mhk",
      "speakerName": "miho",
      "speakerNameEn": "miho",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-miho.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_mhk_04_02/sud_vo_adv_card_mhk_04_02-mhk002.m4a",
      "text": "……はあ？\n何を言っているんですか、貴方は",
      "translations": {
        "en": "…Huh?\nWhat are you talking about?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 10.9656918208,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_summerfes-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "summerfes-00-noon",
      "startTime": 13.253764248
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "mhk",
      "speakerName": "miho",
      "speakerNameEn": "miho",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-miho.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_mhk_04_02/sud_vo_adv_card_mhk_04_02-mhk003.m4a",
      "text": "もし水着を持って来ているのでしたら\n海の水深を確認していただきたいと思ったのですが",
      "translations": {
        "en": "If you brought a swimsuit‚\nI wanted you to check the water depth.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 15.7990251541,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_mhk_04_02/sud_vo_adv_card_mhk_04_02-koh002.m4a",
      "text": "あー……あああ、なるほど",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Ah… I see.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 19.6012699129,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_mhk_04_02/sud_vo_adv_card_mhk_04_02-koh003.m4a",
      "text": "仕事のつもりだったので、水着は持って来てないんです\nmihoさんこそ、水着はないんですか？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "I thought it was work‚ so I didn't bring a swimsuit.\nmiho-san‚ do you have a swimsuit?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 27.5333333333,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_summerfes-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "summerfes-00-noon",
      "startTime": 30.4764175734
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "mhk",
      "speakerName": "miho",
      "speakerNameEn": "miho",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-miho.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_mhk_04_02/sud_vo_adv_card_mhk_04_02-mhk004.m4a",
      "text": "ここに来たのは遊びではなくて、仕事のためです\nそれに、海で着られるような水着も持ってませんし",
      "translations": {
        "en": "We came here for work‚ not to play.\nBesides‚ I don't have a swimsuit suitable for the sea.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 34.2833798117,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_summerfes-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "summerfes-00-noon",
      "startTime": 37.564535459
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "mhk",
      "speakerName": "miho",
      "speakerNameEn": "miho",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-miho.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_mhk_04_02/sud_vo_adv_card_mhk_04_02-mhk005.m4a",
      "text": "……仕方ないですね\n水深は、後でライフセーバーの方に聞いておきます",
      "translations": {
        "en": "…I guess it can't be helped.\nI'll ask the lifeguard about the water depth later.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 39.8105901558,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "mhk",
      "speakerName": "miho",
      "speakerNameEn": "miho",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-miho.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_mhk_04_02/sud_vo_adv_card_mhk_04_02-mhk006.m4a",
      "text": "あと、調べておきたいのは……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Now‚ what else do I need to check…",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 43.1845353128,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_okinawabeach-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "okinawabeach-00-noon",
      "startTime": 46.7417234979
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_okinawabeach-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "okinawabeach-00-noon",
      "startTime": 46.7417234979
    },
    {
      "type": "sfx",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBgm/sud_se_adv_coast-01.m4a",
      "startTime": 46.9750553054
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "mhk",
      "speakerName": "miho",
      "speakerNameEn": "miho",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-miho.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_mhk_04_02/sud_vo_adv_card_mhk_04_02-mhk007.m4a",
      "text": "……ふう。事前に確認したいのは\nおおむねこんなところでしょうか",
      "translations": {
        "en": "…Phew. The main things I needed\nto confirm are done.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 50.7772568225,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_okinawabeach-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "okinawabeach-00-noon",
      "startTime": 53.1455999297
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "mhk",
      "speakerName": "miho",
      "speakerNameEn": "miho",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-miho.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_mhk_04_02/sud_vo_adv_card_mhk_04_02-mhk008.m4a",
      "text": "では、ホテルに向かいましょうか\n調査にまで付き合わせてしまって、すみませんでした",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Let's head to the hotel.\nSorry for dragging you along for the survey.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 55.4772568225,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_mhk_04_02/sud_vo_adv_card_mhk_04_02-koh004.m4a",
      "text": "まだ昼過ぎですし、少し泳いだらいいじゃないですか\nせっかく、海で時間も出来たことですし",
      "translations": {
        "en": "It's still early afternoon‚ why don't you swim a bit?\nSince we have some free time at the sea.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 63.0333333333,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_okinawabeach-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "okinawabeach-00-noon",
      "startTime": 65.8333548787
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "mhk",
      "speakerName": "miho",
      "speakerNameEn": "miho",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-miho.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_mhk_04_02/sud_vo_adv_card_mhk_04_02-mhk009.m4a",
      "text": "さっき、水着は持って来ていないと言ったでしょう",
      "translations": {
        "en": "I already said I didn't bring a swimsuit.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 65.8333548787,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_okinawabeach-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "okinawabeach-00-noon",
      "startTime": 68.8874591909
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_mhk_04_02/sud_vo_adv_card_mhk_04_02-koh005.m4a",
      "text": "汚さないように気を付けてくれれば\n明日の撮影用の衣装を着ていただいて構いませんよ",
      "translations": {
        "en": "If you don't mind being careful‚\nyou can wear tomorrow's outfit.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 70.9612170473,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_mhk_04_02/sud_vo_adv_card_mhk_04_02-koh006.m4a",
      "text": "あれは水着と同じ素材で出来てますし\nちょっと海に入るくらいなら、問題ないと思います",
      "translations": {
        "en": "It's made of the same material as a swimsuit.\nA little dip in the sea shouldn't be a problem.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 77.2333333333,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_okinawabeach-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "okinawabeach-00-noon",
      "startTime": 80.5267562631
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "mhk",
      "speakerName": "miho",
      "speakerNameEn": "miho",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-miho.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_mhk_04_02/sud_vo_adv_card_mhk_04_02-mhk010.m4a",
      "text": "まぁ……休める時には、休むのも大事……と\nしばらく前に、思い知らされましたし",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Well… It's important to rest when you can…\nI realized that a while ago.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 85.4456470011,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_okinawabeach-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "okinawabeach-00-noon",
      "startTime": 88.1559173032
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "mhk",
      "speakerName": "miho",
      "speakerNameEn": "miho",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-miho.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_mhk_04_02/sud_vo_adv_card_mhk_04_02-mhk011.m4a",
      "text": "分かりました\n少し、海でのんびり羽を伸ばしていきます",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Alright.\nI'll relax at the sea for a bit.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 91.6123136678,
      "sfxList": [
        {
          "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBgm/sud_se_adv_zawa-02.m4a",
          "delay": 4310.268808000003,
          "startTime": 95.9225824758
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_summerfes-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "summerfes-00-noon",
      "startTime": 95.6892506683
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_summerfes-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "summerfes-00-noon",
      "startTime": 95.9225824758
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "mhk",
      "speakerName": "miho",
      "speakerNameEn": "miho",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-miho.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_mhk_04_02/sud_vo_adv_card_mhk_04_02-mhk012.m4a",
      "text": "人が増えてきましたね……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "There are more people now…",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 97.689226827,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_summerfes-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "summerfes-00-noon",
      "startTime": 100.1351180635
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_mhk_04_02/sud_vo_adv_card_mhk_04_02-koh007.m4a",
      "text": "平日とはいえ、夏休み期間ですからね\nこの時期に人が来なけりゃ、海は商売あがったりです",
      "translations": {
        "en": "It's summer vacation‚ even on a weekday.\nIf visitors didn't come now‚ the beach would be out of business.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 104.0666631062,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_summerfes-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "summerfes-00-noon",
      "startTime": 107.6284511489
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "mhk",
      "speakerName": "miho",
      "speakerNameEn": "miho",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-miho.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_mhk_04_02/sud_vo_adv_card_mhk_04_02-mhk013.m4a",
      "text": "……ところで、私に遊んでこいとはおっしゃいましたが\nなんで、まだ{user}さんがいるんです",
      "translations": {
        "en": "…By the way‚ you told me to go play‚\nbut why are {user}-san still here?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 111.7938516454,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "mhk",
      "speakerName": "miho",
      "speakerNameEn": "miho",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-miho.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_mhk_04_02/sud_vo_adv_card_mhk_04_02-mhk014.m4a",
      "text": "ロケ地の調査は終わったのですから\nホテルに戻って、明日の準備をしてはいかがですか",
      "translations": {
        "en": "We've finished the location survey.\nWhy don't you go back to the hotel and prepare for tomorrow?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 117.4938516454,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_summerfes-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "summerfes-00-noon",
      "startTime": 120.9260926806
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_mhk_04_02/sud_vo_adv_card_mhk_04_02-koh008.m4a",
      "text": "（mihoさんを一人で放り出す訳にはいかない）\n（……と言うと、多分また嫌がるだろうし）",
      "translations": {
        "en": "（I can't just leave miho-san alone.）\n（…But she'll probably dislike it if I say that.）",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 124.3878334073,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_summerfes-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "summerfes-00-noon",
      "startTime": 127.9113760873
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_mhk_04_02/sud_vo_adv_card_mhk_04_02-koh009.m4a",
      "text": "いや、俺も少しくらい海を満喫しようと思いまして……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Well‚ I thought I might enjoy the sea a bit too…",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 127.9113760873,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "mhk",
      "speakerName": "miho",
      "speakerNameEn": "miho",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-miho.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_mhk_04_02/sud_vo_adv_card_mhk_04_02-mhk015.m4a",
      "text": "人に、遊べだのなんだのと言っておいて\n結局、自分が海で遊びたかっただけじゃないですか",
      "translations": {
        "en": "You told me to go play‚\nbut you just wanted to enjoy the sea yourself.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 135.4124913371,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_summerfes-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "summerfes-00-noon",
      "startTime": 138.8347318891
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
